\alpha = 3dz
dx\wedge dy + 4dx\wedge dz = dx\wedge(dy + 4dz).
dz\wedge(dy+4dz) = dz\wedge dy + 4dz\wedge dz = dz\wedge dy.
(dx + 3dz)\wedge(dy + 4dz) = dx\wedge dy + 4dx\wedge dz + 3dz\wedge dy.
